msgid "Delete the selection."
msgstr "Suprimiu la selecció."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:190
msgid "Here you can search in the text."
msgstr "Aquí podreu cercar en el text."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:192
msgid "And navigate up or down in the text."
msgstr "I navegar amunt o avall en el text."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:197
msgid "Silence detection"
msgstr "Detecció de silenci"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:199
msgid "This works with the VOSK engine only."
msgstr "Això només funciona en el motor VOSK."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:201
msgid ""
"Open the clip in the clip monitor and open the speech editor window (:"
"menuselection:`View --> Speech Editor`) ."
msgstr ""
"Obriu el clip en el monitor de clips i obriu la finestra de l'editor de veu "
"(:menuselection:`Vista --> Editor de veu`)."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:203
msgid ""
"Select your language or :ref:`install_language` and download the model for "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu l'idioma o :ref:`install_language` i baixeu el model per a ell."

# skip-rule: t-sp_2p,t-2p_sp
#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:205
msgid "Then click :guilabel:`Start Recognition` button."
msgstr "Feu clic al botó :guilabel:`Inicia el reconeixement`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:207
msgid ""
"Once this is done, click on the time-code where no-speech is indicated and "
"just hit the :kbd:`delete` key. Repeat the operation for all the parts you "
"want to remove, including where someone says what you don't want to listen "
"in your final edit."
msgstr ""
"Una vegada fet això, feu clic en el codi de temps on no s'indica la veu i "
"simplement premeu la tecla :kbd:`Supr`. Repetiu l'operació per a totes les "
"parts que vulgueu eliminar, incloent on algú diu el que no voleu escoltar en "
"la vostra edició final."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:209
msgid ""
"Once finished, make sure :guilabel:`Selected zone only` is disabled, click "
"on the :guilabel:`Save` button on the lower left part of the speech editor "
"window and after few seconds a new playlist is added in the project bin "
"without silence and without the text you don't want."
msgstr ""
"Un cop acabat, assegureu-vos que :guilabel:`Només la zona seleccionada` està "
"desactivada, feu clic al botó :guilabel:`Desa` a la part inferior esquerra "
"de la finestra de l'editor de veu i després de pocs segons s'afegirà una "
"llista de reproducció nova a la safata del projecte sense silenci i sense el "
"text que no voleu."
